---
title: Golden Tofu and Quinoa Bowl with Edamame, Carrot-Cabbage Slaw and Peanut Dressing
description: This Asian-inspired quinoa and tofu bowl is hearty and filling. Tofu cubes get pan-fried to get a nice crust, and a peanut dressing is the perfect coating on these golden cubes.
